title: Master Security
text:
This is a Quarto website.
To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.
We base our Initiative: Master Security on Planning a <Minumum Viable Nothing (MVN)|https://github.com/vanHeemstraSystems/minimum-viable-nothing>.

Identify and understand the Business Needs.


Determine the long-term goal of the product (i.e., good or service) and write it down.
Answer the question “Why are we doing this project?”
Identify the success criteria that will indicate whether or not the product (i.e., good or service) is successful.
